message.body: So how was your night out of the hospital
good. Went so ham this weekend lol
Haha. Nice
What u end up soon??
Doin*
Well right now I'm in Georgia. And then when I get back I have to work two doubles but I'm off wed and thurs
What ya doin in ga?
Visiting my aunt/escaping my parents/escaping my feelings (the last one did not go over so well) I saw a lizard today
Where in ga does she live
Gray
So how do u like it. Sounds like u in the country!!
It's nice! It's humid. And it's pretty boring. Be better if I had some company.
Especially for the drive home
u drove alone??
Yep
Dam and I can't even get u to come to the city lol
That's cause the city's dummmmbb
13hrs to ga?
Bahahaha. I'll come to the city. I just haven't had two consecutive days off. But I do next week!
What days?
Wednesday and Thursday
Workin memorial day??
Yea. Double.
Mayb that's money making day
I'm not sure. I hope. It is chestnut hill
What restaurant??
Iron hill
Yea it looks nice!!
It is. It's really a decent place to work at. The only part that sucks is there is absolutely no calling out. You either have to have a drs note or find
someone to pick the shift up
Yea and work in weekends always stinks!!
This is true. I'm trying to get a second job. Not sure where yet though
Dam u hustlin
I need to move out of my parents house. They make me miserable and they're holding me back from so much
Oh yea for sure. Do u have a lotta college debt? U 24?
Oh yes. 30000. And yes. I'm 24
How much is that a month
About 400
U dun mind a roommate right??
At this point no I don't.
U should walk dogs for extra money
Hit up craigslist!!
I don't really like dogs. Nor do I really know how to get started with it. I could see of I could get my babysitting gig back but I'm not sure. I haven't
talked to then in a while
I don't wanna live with someone I don't really know.
Hmm yea I dun like that either
Yea. It's be strange. I'd rather live alone. I was considering moving with my friend joe but he just recently turned into a jerk face so that's out. Need
to find a new one or a really cheap apartment
Could u do studio
So are we hanging out Wednesday
I don't think I'd want to do a studio. I'm always trapped in my room at home so I don't want to feel the same way on my own
Dam girl u better start making some money. Yeah if u come down the city!
Well you'd have to let me crash cause I'm not driving there. Parkings ridiculous
No problem
Sweet
when do u leave georgia
Saturday.
U have cousins??
Not in Georgia. Just my aunt and uncle.
Is it blazing hot? I see I have a pool tho!!
It's really humid. Like disgustingly humid
Better stay by that pool then
Haha. It's nice but it really is boring
Like nothing's in walking distance
Do they have an accent??
My uncle does cause he's from Georgia. My aunt has a weird accent. They've lived in so many places that I think she's created her own signature accent. (
She's from Philly)
Haha that's cool. U guys close?
Yea. She's my godmom. We're extremely alike it's scary.
U having a good time then??
It's alright. She's had to work the past two days so I haven't done much. She's off tomorrow so were going out. It was suppose to be like a mind clearing
trip but I kinda just wanna punch someone in the face. Preferably my ex boyfriend and his new girlfriend.
Well hopefully those feelings will subside
I hope. It's been three months. I feel so pathetic. And the worst is he even said to me yesterday someone told him I was all fucked up over it, as if I'm
not already embarrassed enough
You gonna be fine. Trust me I been there
Thanks. It just sucks. Anyway. You have to work Wednesday or Thursday next week
Yeah I actually just remembered. I have the follow up for my study at 7am Thursday the 29. I can't do wed night. Thurs not good for u?
Nah. I have a double Friday
Dam we never can figure out a good time!
Maaaaaan. Next time. I have two weekends off in June at the end of we can't do anything prior. I'm supposed to go to the shore but I probably won't be th
ere all the days I took off
When's Ur morning shift start?
What time do you have to be at the hospital
Like 720 or something
And I have to fast 8 hrs beforehand
Oh no. Well I mean im off all day Wednesday. We could still do something
I mean I work throughout the day
Aw. Boooooo
The budget is in constant need of my analyis
Haha. Well this stinks
Did u take off those days or just happened to be off
Just happened to be off. I'm a double Monday Tuesday Friday. Work Saturday and Sunday morning
Yeah this study def been messing up my social life lol
Well figure something out. I would say maybe Tuesday night but that'd all depends on when I get done work
Yeah Tues would work for me most likely. Ur on a double that day?
Yea. I'll have to see what time I get done and how I feel. Last double I worked 13 hours and I woke up in the middle of the night from my legs throbbing
Damn they working u hard over there!!
Yea. Well it's graduation week. But lat Tuesday I was home at 9 so I'll have to see how the day/night pans out
And then we can have fuuuuuuuun
Lol indeed. I wouldn't think Tuesdays would be crazy busy
Lets hope they're not so we can hang. I haven't seen you in years
Yeah I know. I can't believe I was Applebees 3 yrs ago almost 4
Oh goodness! It really is crazy when you think about it.
Yeah u were like too young for bars back then
I know. But I'm all grown up now!
I know. I wonder what grown up jess is like
Well. I think I'm a lot less fun. But I still have my sense of humor.
Lol why do u say Ur not as fun?
Well I'm still trying to get back to who I am. And I don't get as drunk as I used to cause I'm still getting back to that from when i had my stomach problem.
But I guess I can be fun. I just never have the ideas to initiate a plan I guess
Oh yeah I forgot about that stomach problem. Was is acid reflux?
Chronic gastritis. Took forever to go away but it still messed me up mentally. I've been drinking more now though to prove I can. That's my new outlook on life
I hope Ur being safe!
So where is it you're working at
Oh I am. I don't drink that much and often. Just more than I was. I was so scared to do it for like two years
I work at the Philadelphia school district as a budget analyst
Oh that's right! You told me that a while ago. You still hang with Tom and Harrison
yeah goin on three years. Tom Wrigley? And yup
Ohhhhhhhh. Yes. That's who I was talking about. That's cool.
Didn't know u knew tom
Yea. We met two or three times through you.
He's a douche. Haha
what? Y u say that. Hes one of my best friends!
I think we might be thinkin of diff ppl
Hahaha. I know he's one of your best friends. And no were not. Tall skinny guy. Blonde hair. Actor. He was douchey the one night I met him. He's alright.
Nah that'd dave . Toms brother
Ohhhh. I met Tom too. Oh wait. Toms the one who has the girlfriend. He's been dating her for a really log time right?
Yep. Much less duchy than dave
Yes! He was a lot nicer. Sorry I got them mixed up. You were really good friends with Dave though. Like better friends with him than Tom back then
Do you remember that one new ears when we kissed
Sry I was asleep. Yea Dave moved to Chicago though and started a new life. Nye at vals?
Woah. And nye at sans. I guess we're talking about the same place
Dave is getting married. Proposing this Sunday
Whaaaat?! That's awesome. One of the last times I saw him he judged like every girl we were with so that's great that he found someone
Lol yep. I only met her once
Well good for him! I need people I know to get married. I need some weddings to go to
Lol u never gonna see them again then
I'm ok with that. I don't see them now. So it wouldn't make a difference
yea thats how I feel bout dave
